Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真廣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.23,0:01:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想這麼問我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能成為我的女人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 我還不至於那麼沒品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你到底想和妹妹變成什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:01:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從沒把我當哥哥看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又沒血緣關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 為什麼會是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.78,0:02:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不合理了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一直以來交往過的女生完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒姿色又沒胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會對你那麼在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越想越不淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是睡眠不足哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你暫時不要和別人扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖聽我話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我已經和某人扯上關係了 你會怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難…難道你已經有男朋友了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照合理思維來想的話 到底有沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是愛指引著命運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是命運指引著愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥冥之中考驗著我們的人生之難題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.82,每集標題,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(643,476)}初吻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防寒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓寒風滲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉風小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說決戰前得好好養養神什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又是喝醉了 睡的正香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪裡弄到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從上次我們借宿的人家裡借來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:04:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真厲害 見縫插針的神偷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是借用一下而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用完會還回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一切結束之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切…結束之後？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管結果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的不合理之事將會馬上被糾正
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦找到殺死愛花的兇手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真廣一定會毫不猶豫地親手了結他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的真廣就只為此而活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇完畢之後再做何打算呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久不見你這樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前老盯著手機看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近幾乎不這樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是冷得火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天很悶熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花啊 你還有這麼多作業沒做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大暑假的不讓人好好休息 還一大堆作業
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不合理了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夏天結束之前試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我可不想在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼想來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是想挑個好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野有什麼建議嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 突然問我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 愛花有什麼想法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別墅？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年暑假的最後一周 我們全家都會一起過的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要叫我也去那裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父母肯定會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 居然要和真廣一起住一周啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也和我一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野 請你和真廣好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和那人交朋友的 也只有吉野你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:07:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經察覺到真廣的心意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真廣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閒著吧 現在到車站來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別突然就一口咬定我很閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 10分鐘後見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分鐘？  這也太趕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.89,0:07:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真廣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹一下 這傢伙叫瀧川吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野君？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不常見的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…我果然還有事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那咱們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold不住了 我萌上姐弟戀了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.63,Default top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是和同齡人交往好無趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真廣 這麼做不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.32,Default top,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好又怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中紅心！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帥爆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 兩個人都好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是職業級別的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BYE BYE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再做這種事了 我會很頭大的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家難得想給你介紹個女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰拜託過你那種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的還真是輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙的性格我要不多管管 什麼時候才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友可不是想要找一個才去交往的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才想讓她成為自己的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是戀愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時間才回家 還真是悠閒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓吉野陪了我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他差不多也該想找個妹子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想給他介紹一個來著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他貌似很不情願的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種人的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該和吉野同學合不來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話可不能這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身邊可是有幾位妙齡女大學生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想用筷子戳你的鎖骨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性情怪癖到會說這種話的吉野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得妙齡女大學生會受得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對吉野這小子也太多偏見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好聽點 吉野同學是適應性強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不好聽點 就是沒個性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論身處多麼惡劣的環境
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都能處之泰然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己卻不會積極主動地去改變現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是那種主動出擊 把女生追到手的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反倒要女生倒過來追他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的女生遇上這種不乾脆的人 避之不及呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那倒也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吉野相配的應該是像你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:11:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放蕩不羈 我行我素
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都按照自己的想法行事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人被你耍得團團轉 你卻完全不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟王公貴族一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野和你這種人在一起再合適不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這麼噁心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是說男人之間的交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是 這世上沒有女生能像你這麼傲慢專橫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖這麼說 你還是要好好珍惜吉野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.82,0:11:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為無論發生什麼 他都會和你並肩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是服了真廣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說他已經覺察到我和愛花的事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才硬要給我介紹對像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 應該不會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙明明第六感很強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可關鍵時候卻很遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對兄妹真是太會捉弄人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:14.84,sign 黑體,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\frz6.419\pos(672,542)}女大學生的鎖骨怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你的感官那麼敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼敏感不敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是富家公子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愛炫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是和自己喜歡的女生交往的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把人追到手上了也沒什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過…那種話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:13:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…我還是不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為總是別人先找我搭訕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和自己喜歡的女孩交往是什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.95,0:13:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管交往得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終還是會分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和自己喜歡的人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還去考慮這些問題不是太殘酷了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星 真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也一起看過星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我家的別墅嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 暑假的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 你不是說過討厭星星的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡冬天的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.18,0:13:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜然威嚴而又冷艷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近在眼前卻又高高在上觸手不及
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真廣可能一生都察覺不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己只是喜歡上了愛花
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣狂妄的真廣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍碰觸到愛花都會緊張到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在她身邊卻又會不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花雖然嘴上沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定也不討厭真廣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們不是如此相遇 或許他們會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 真廣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！ 真是麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力所能及的事就要自己動手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是爸爸的教育方針哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你父母竟然不能過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 因為有工作走不開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 吉野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有空的話 把樓梯也擦一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是討厭吉野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才請那傢伙來別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情的玩弄他 拿他來解悶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說 你有什麼陰謀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陰謀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還真有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭丫頭 一下子放那麼多的話會烤焦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真廣才是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該刷好醬料再烤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦算啦 享受美食時就開心點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來烤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.34,0:16:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來烤玉米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也想吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.50,sign 黑體,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\c&H414141&\frz8.922\pos(654,629)}吃完飯後 我們在後院碰面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤焦了啊 吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們居住的城鎮裡 看不到這麼美的星空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒看過這麼多的星星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是要溢出天空一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日的星空真是很沒節操呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡亂一氣地閃耀著光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花討厭星星嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拚命炫耀自己的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望在自己逝去的瞬間 有人能意識到自己存在過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡這種耿直的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野 你在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花也在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野 你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們搞什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩撲克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來別墅玩當然首選撲克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那輸了的人就得做早餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要摻一腳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你們倆剛才在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我拿夏季的星星很沒轍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無節操的亂閃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脖子有點癢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請調成振動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 氣死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你玩撲克這麼厲害啊 為啥一直那麼低調
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種彫蟲小技 沒必要顯擺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花也很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.38,sign 黑體,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs42\frz350.292\3c&H414141&\pos(653,516)\c&HD6D6DA&}已調成振動模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明腦子沒我好使
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好不要和愛花兩個人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花這丫頭滿腦子邪惡的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識她起就一直這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道那傢伙在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻薄又不招人喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時還想根本沒法和這種女的一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 她不知不覺地就融入了我們家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺就融入進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 到底在想些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花在想些什麼 你很想知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因為很邪惡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.97,0:19:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對愛花…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啥 這樣算的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星期的早餐都歸你包了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真廣那動物般的第六感 會不會察覺到我們的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話就永遠沒法接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為你不能像個男人那樣強硬一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花 這樣很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵們都在看著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛花…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野 差不多該上路了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我對魔具沒什麼興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過決戰真讓人熱血沸騰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼害怕做啥 我怎麼可能朝你開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決心不過是記憶的奴隸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨記憶可以幻化成萬物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:56.27,Default 備註,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《哈姆雷特》中第三幕第二場台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈姆雷特嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:21:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天這復仇劇也該落幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明的天空已裹上了赤褐色的外衣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.94,0:22:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏著那東方高山上的露水走過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:13.57,Default 備註,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《哈姆雷特》第一章第一場台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.30,0:22:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.43,0:24:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得今天會有什麼變化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.91,0:24:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是決一雌雄的時候了 左門
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.02,0:24:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.45,0:24:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就讓我來了斷你的好運
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.81,0:24:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此這個世界會隕滅一次
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了啊 絕園之樹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.65,0:24:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要…只要能復仇就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.02,0:24:27.51,每集標題,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(563,484)}魔女斷頭之時
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.51,0:24:28.51,每集标题,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(595,576)}
